sequenceDiagram
    participant W as Workload
    participant V as Verifier
    participant KS as Key Store
    note over W, KS: Credential Acquisition Phase
    W->>W: Generate Asymmetric<br/>Encryption Key
    W->>W: Generate Evidence<br/>(incl. Public Encryption Key)
    W->>V: Request Attestation (Evidence)
    V->>V: Check Evidence against Reference Values
    V->>V: Compute Attestation Results
    V->>W: Return Attestation Results<br/>(incl. Encryption Key)
    W->>KS: Request Credential Key (Attestation Results)
    KS->>KS: Validate Attestation Results<br/>against Credential Key Release Policy
    KS->>KS: Encrypt Credential Key<br/>to Encryption Key
    KS->>W: Return Encrypted Credential Key
    W->>W: Decrypt Credential Key
